  "texts": [
    "(ii) Add an overall minus sign for each type-II vertex and for each propagator connecting two type-II vertices.",
    "(iii) Draw a positive-energy cut on each propagator going from a type-I vertex to a type-II vertex.",
    "Additionally, flip the iε in each propagator connecting two type-II vertices.",
    "More explicitly, apply the replacement rule1 p 2 + m 2 -iε → 2πiδ + (p 2 + m 2)for each prop.",
    "going from I to II, (p 2 + m 2 + iε) -1 for each prop."
